He means the Manicheans. There is a Manichean 
sentiment lurking in some souls, as though the
intercourse of the sexes were a necessary evil, only
permissible because inevitable, but a bad act in itself.
They should take to heart St Augustine's saying:
"He does not perfectly believe in Thee, O Lord,
who objects to any creature that Thou hast made."<p>


